name: Business Performance Dashboard
description: I specialize in creating custom Power BI solutions that help businesses track performance and make data-driven decisions. My services include data setup and integration from multiple sources, data modeling for efficient reporting, and the development of custom dashboards that focus on key business and sales performance metrics. I also add interactive features like filters and drill-throughs for deeper analysis, allowing you to monitor overall business performance and identify areas for improvement. Let me help you turn your data into actionable insights with tailored Power BI dashboards
